5:
Whoa, look at the turnout! And it's
not even Halloween yet.
8:
This should make capturing another
specimen a piece of cake—er,
candy!
12:
You really think there are ghosts in a
crowded place like this?
15:
According to my research, they tend
to gather at parties and other
crowded events, contrary to what
you might have heard.
17:
Perhaps they're just naturally
attracted to human emotions. 
Or maybe there's a magnetic field 
that pulls them in. Who knows?
20:
Huh. I didn't know you researched
the supernatural too.
28:
Science and the supernatural may
be like oil and water, but statistics
never lie.
31:
Statistics? You mean like... ghost
sightings?
35:
Precisely. No matter how you spin it,
data is data. If so many people
claim to have seen something, it
can't be ignored!
39: It's all part of the scientific method!
42:
So you're saying the existence of
ghosts can be proven by science?
49:
It's well-known that ghosts are
formed from lingering resentments
of the dead, but nobody wants to
help me experiment.
56:
Yup! Just think of it as, er, emotional
residue! Something that'll
emotionally cool off and fade away.
58:
Of course, we're only talking in
hypotheticals, since it technically
hasn't been proven that a soul
actually—
61:
Oops, sorry! Got carried away again,
didn't I?
63:
You're just such an honor student,
Alk—I couldn't help it!
68:
Careful, Alk. Her praise can only lead
to no good.
73:
And you're quite the lovely
specimen yourself, Light...
82:
Eeeyargh! I-I already said I didn't
have any candy! I'm sorry!
89:
The Boogie Catcher's responding!
Let's move!
95:
Perhaps this was the spirit of
someone who died of starvation... 
Or someone too sick to eat.
104: That old thing? I threw it out.
113:
Who needs that, when you've got
THIS!
126:
Oh, don't look directly into the light,
'kay?
131: Tell me that sooner next time!
139: Boom! And that's how it's done!
148:
I can't believe it. And you didn't even
need to use your ghost-capturing
machine or anything!
153:
Don't ever estimate the power of
science!
155:
And to be honest, I forgot to charge
it...
158:
I don't know if we can chalk this one
up to the power of science...
161:
Okay! Let's ride this momentum and
round up a few more while we're at
it!
169:
You'll help too, right, Alk? 
I'll make it worth your while...
177:
Quick to the draw, aren't you? 
I knew they'd grow on you.
180:
Anyway, I'm kidding about the
candy. I'll find something else for ya!
182:
Come on, you two! Those ghosts
aren't gonna capture themselves!
